channel.title: Goliath RsPs! 317 Client Revised!
channel.description:
Hey everyone, I'm a player from Goliath RsPs![url=http://goliath-ps.com/]http://goliath-ps.com/[/url] It's a great friendly community that is looking for new players now! It's content packed, 317 loading higher revision, Goliath-PS, Auto-donations, auto-vote, Donator XP Boosts, Nex, 100+ Achievements, and much more! Eventually looking for staff members! After we get to a certain number of players, a staff position will be given out to a random, worthy player. Come join now in all the fun! I promise you'll have just as much fun as I am. So, its a great, friendly, and all around amazing community, especially when we get a lot of players rolling on in. Have fun guys and enjoy, plus you get up to 8 vote scroll per voting period! thats crazy good. 1m and 1 vote point, or 10mins of 30% xp bonus!
[center][font=times new roman][size=24pt]IMPORTANT![/size][/font][/center] [spoiler]Friendly thing though, our VPN is about to run out, we need a total of $75 to keep the server alive and running! We only have 3 days to save the server! Also, about another $10 to renew the site. But, who can help keep the server alive will receive an extra gift for saving the server![/spoiler]
